Package: glaredb
Title: R Bindings for 'GlareDB'
Version: 0.0.2.9000
Authors@R:
    c(person("Tatsuya", "Shima", email = "ts1s1andn@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
URL: https://github.com/eitsupi/r-glaredb
BugReports: https://github.com/eitsupi/r-glaredb/issues
Description:
    R bindings for 'GlareDB', an analytical database based on 'Apache Arrow' and
    'Apache DataFusion' that can connect to various data sources and execute queries.
